WORK SUMMARY:
Learned about NPM (Node Package Manager) and package management in Node.js projects. Understood how to initialize a project using npm init, install dependencies
with npm install, and manage packages using package.json. Practiced creating a basic server using the built-in http module to handle client requests and send responses. 
This session helped in understanding the basic working of a Node.js server.


LEARNING OUTCOMES :
Learned how to initialize and manage Node.js projects using NPM.
Understood the purpose of package.json, node_modules, and dependency management.
Gained practical understanding of creating a basic server using the http module and handling client requests.
